{"tid":827372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土研究社】全港有301公頃未善用官地 面積相當於1.7 個粉嶺高爾夫球場","createTime":"2018-09-19T01:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T03:02:42.000Z","uid":138409,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"94ccb21dd2a6e10802b48a5c5bec32e96b4c39bb","tid":827372,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:23:45.000Z","msg":"雖然最近打完颱風 監督政府善後工作固然緊要<br />\n但係都唔好忘記「土地大辯論」依然響度進行緊㗎<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/1978191588943571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fposts%2F1978191588943571&d=9siJFAaRUHZW6EtVwHtQSk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a28f76d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/1978191588943571</a><br />\n<br />\n【有得睇啦】《隱藏選項：香港臨時使用及閒置官地研究》報告正式上線!<br />\n<br />\n呢個研究報告最大既發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">區區都搵到加埋532塊有成301公頃成5,000呎以上既「未善用官地」，成1.7個粉嶺高爾夫球場咁大</span>，唔係臨時泊下車、放下鐵馬就係曬緊太陽，長期都係唔善用既官地黎，直接揭破政府成日話中短期冇地解決土地問題，根本就係學地產商賣樓咁「擠牙膏」!<br />\n<br />\n土地大辯論成5個月，呢堆「未善用官地」既土地資訊一直隱藏左到今日，呢個選項一開始就被政府DQ左，市民冇得揀呢啲地做各種用地，變左好似成日冇地揀咁款，咪逼左大家揀佢心目中既公私合營同移山填海計劃，真係香港地 小人多!<br />\n<br />\n我地花左半年既心血，除左寫左呢份報告出黎，同時亦都建立左全港首個未善用官地清單及空間資料庫，一塊一塊咁勾畫出黎架，大家一齊睇下以下連結慢慢欣賞，唔阻大家!"},{"pid":"9ed6d5c4990d0dd47bb4b887554feba4d0d94b3a","tid":827372,"uid":159234,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:26:44.000Z","msg":"on99頭痛醫頭腳痛醫腳  呢d地用得幾耐<br />\n梗係一次過解決未來五六十年土地供應問題<br />\n支持大規模填海<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f4f7f8b73f0bfa34b3cd7142ba5de455f6c323","tid":827372,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed6d5c4990d0dd47bb4b887554feba4d0d94b3a","tid":827372,"uid":159234,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:26:44.000Z","msg":"on99頭痛醫頭腳痛醫腳  呢d地用得幾耐<br />\n梗係一次過解決未來五六十年土地供應問題<br />\n支持大規模填海<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:28:20.000Z","msg":"無人話過淨係靠呢啲官地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5ee9514a06282d0a324f75e7cbd677fbd565ae","tid":827372,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:32:23.000Z","msg":"四大潛在用途:合共 532 幅、301 公頃未善用官地,研究團隊建議可作四大用途滿足現時逼<br />\n切的需要:<br />\n<br />\n○ <span style=\"color: blue;\">發展</span><span style=\"color: red;\">過渡性</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">房屋</span>:<br />\n<br />\n根據社聯早前有關估算,每 0.1 公頃的土地能夠興建 90 個貨櫃屋單<br />\n位作過渡性房屋,若只利用三分一未善用官地(約 100 公頃),保守估計可提供約<br />\n90,000 個貨櫃屋單位,相當於現時 92,700 個劏房數目;<br />\n<br />\n○ <span style=\"color: blue;\">社福設施:</span><br />\n<br />\n研究團隊發現,只要 50 公頃未實現的「政府、機構或社區」用地,興建單<br />\n幢式長者日間護理中心及安老院舍,即能原區提供 12 萬個名額,滿足《安老服務計劃<br />\n方案》估算的未來三十年社區及院舍照顧服務需求。另外,動用約 30 公頃的閒置「鄉<br />\n村式發展」官地興建社福設施,亦能舒緩鄉郊地方缺乏休憩和社福用地的問題;<br />\n<br />\n○ <span style=\"color: blue;\">康體設施:</span><br />\n<br />\n根據《香港規劃標準與準則》地盤面積 0.6 公頃標準計算,運用 30 公頃未<br />\n善用官地,即可興建 43 個體育中心,解決現時各區康體設施不足問題;<br />\n<br />\n○ <span style=\"color: blue;\">多層式發展/一地多用:</span><br />\n<br />\n採用「一地多用」的多層發展模式,將未善用官地上的低效<br />\n率 和未盡其用的設施,或露天停車場整合,以騰空社區珍貴土地資源。<br />\n<br />\n● <span style=\"color: blue;\">對應</span><span style=\"color: red;\">中短期</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">土地需求:</span><br />\n<br />\n本研究發現,這些未善用官地多在規劃上屬於「政府、機構或社區」<br />\n(G/IC)用地及「休憩用地」(O),並多位於市區,可中短期內對應各種社福及康體用地短缺,<br />\n亦可毋須經過改劃,短期內提供臨時房屋,解決急切的居住問題。"},{"pid":"a53aa4e57a3bcf195b5c355738e8828177b9ec45","tid":827372,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:36:10.000Z","msg":"人口先係問題"},{"pid":"fc6a07075147166e25bdd6144c027a3324a1c6c2","tid":827372,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/094507_faaa36c255dd14231bb2477cf9eecf7c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F094507_faaa36c255dd14231bb2477cf9eecf7c.png&h=93639ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">名詞解釋</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">「短期租約」</span>(Short-term Tenancy,簡稱「STT」),<br />\n將政府用地臨時出租予個人、商業機構或非政府機構<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/094432_90d8b0ad162c7e2f393296e1174ec7df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F094432_90d8b0ad162c7e2f393296e1174ec7df.png&h=8ba82fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/094440_dee4373af8a028b4be8dfd7f3833f470.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F094440_dee4373af8a028b4be8dfd7f3833f470.png&h=94efef98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">「臨時政府撥地」</span>(Temporary Government Land Allocation,簡稱「TGLA」)<br />\n將政府用地撥給政策局或政府部門作短期用途 (如下圖);<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/094450_9cebd6fe19f3d970513dc61a32621a6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F094450_9cebd6fe19f3d970513dc61a32621a6e.png&h=2675c02f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">未批租或撥用</span>(Unleased or Unallocated)政府土地,<br />\n即「空置官地」"},{"pid":"cb843827e8022158d0c918f57ffe3134949bff3d","tid":827372,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:00:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"372f103ffe13394e29a8aa5aba08ce6da1e1b6ba","tid":827372,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8112936c3a0588683b955b39d47b3f898905c935","tid":827372,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b91e03594b1a8cd40b1d9313d1d46df8344dce2e","tid":827372,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"push"}]}